  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OAInputImage

    public class InputImage
extends InputElement
    Form submit button that uses an image.

    Note: automatically submits on click. sends name.x & name.y name values, and stores in the OAFormSubmitEvent, and can be accessed using the onSubmit* methods.
